Subject: [PATCH 110/113] dt-bindings: Add DT bindings for Toshiba TC358762
 DSI-to-DPI bridge

Add DT bindings for Toshiba TC358762 DSI-to-DPI bridge, this
one is used in the Raspberry Pi 7" touchscreen display unit.

